<h1 id="heroTitle">Luxury Services</h1>
  <div class="tagline" id="heroTagline">Hotel-level care for private residences – immaculate, calm, discreet.</div>
  <p class="lead" id="heroText">A high-end property only feels complete when its condition reflects its architecture. This service is designed exactly for that purpose: as an elegant optional addition to Property Care for owners who expect not only supervision, but visibly flawless presentation.</p>

  <div class="contentBlock" id="serviceTextBlocks">
    <h2 class="sectionTitle">Cleaning for homes that deserve more</h2>
    <p class="sectionPara">A truly clean property changes the entire atmosphere of a space. The air feels clearer, bathrooms feel calmer, surfaces reflect light more beautifully and the overall impression becomes more refined. This is more than routine cleaning. It is the visible quality of a home that is treated with care.</p>
    <p class="sectionPara">We clean private residences in Madeira where “good enough” is not an option. Villas, refined apartments and design-led homes require a level of attention that matches their standard. In properties of this kind, it is not enough to remove visible dirt. What matters is restoring the quiet clarity and polished presence that belong to the home.</p>
    <p class="sectionPara">In high-end residences, quality is not created by architecture alone. It is also created by the condition in which rooms are experienced: flawless surfaces, perfectly prepared bathrooms, streak-free glass, clean edges and an atmosphere that feels composed and under control. This is where our service makes the difference.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="contentBlock">
    <h2 class="sectionTitle">An optional package alongside Property Care</h2>
    <p class="sectionPara">Property Care and premium cleaning belong together, but they are not the same service. Property Care provides continuity, oversight and protection. It ensures that your property remains supervised and cared for during periods of absence. Our Luxury Services package complements that foundation wherever a visibly elevated standard of presentation is required.</p>
    <p class="sectionPara">For this reason, the service is intentionally structured as an optional package. Owners can add it to Property Care before an arrival, after a longer absence or at regular intervals whenever a hotel-level result is desired. There is no overlap, only a clear connection: Property Care keeps the property under control, Luxury Services brings it to perfection.</p>
    <p class="sectionPara">That combination creates real value. The residence is not only looked after and protected, but ready when needed – calm, immaculate and prepared in the way a refined private home should be.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="contentBlock">
    <h2 class="sectionTitle">Our premium standard</h2>
    <p class="sectionPara">We work in a structured way so that the result remains consistently high. Quality is not left to mood or improvisation. It follows a clear sequence of steps and ends with a final control.</p>
    <ul class="sectionList">
      <li>Bathrooms &amp; sanitary areas: hygienic, polished and free from residue</li>
      <li>Kitchen: surfaces, fronts and appliances cared for with precision</li>
      <li>Glass &amp; mirrors: streak-free and ready for daylight</li>
      <li>Touchpoints disinfected: switches, handles, remotes and frequently used contact areas</li>
      <li>Floors completed in full, including edges, transitions and corners</li>
      <li>Final quality check before completion</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="sectionPara">This standard is tailored specifically to high-end residential property. We do not work against the character of a home, but with it. The result should not merely look freshly cleaned. It should feel naturally perfect.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="contentBlock">
    <h2 class="sectionTitle">Respect for materials</h2>
    <p class="sectionPara">Luxury often lives in materials that require understanding. Natural stone, oiled wood, dark fronts, delicate metals, high-end fittings or custom-made surfaces do not respond well to aggressive routines or unsuitable products. That is why every residence is handled with material awareness and respect for its value.</p>
    <p class="sectionPara">Our goal is not simply cleanliness. It is the long-term preservation of beauty and substance. A premium surface should not only be clean after service – it should look calm, cared for and consistent with the standard of the property itself.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="contentBlock">
    <h2 class="sectionTitle">Optional: arrival preparation</h2>
    <p class="sectionPara">When you, your family or your guests arrive, the home should feel right from the first moment. That is why we offer arrival preparation that goes beyond ordinary cleaning. Rooms are prepared so that the property immediately conveys freshness, order and quiet ease – as though everything had just been perfectly reset.</p>
    <p class="sectionPara">Owners who use Madeira as a second home especially value this difference. Instead of starting an arrival by dealing with details, you enter a home that is already ready. That sense of ease is part of true luxury.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="contentBlock">
    <h2 class="sectionTitle">Structure instead of chance – professional cleaning with a system</h2>
    <p class="sectionPara">Where a property needs to be prepared regularly for arrivals, the quality of cleaning influences more than the first impression. It affects stability, organisation and the ability to deliver a consistently high standard. For that reason, our professional cleaning in Madeira does not follow an improvised system. It is based on clearly defined procedures, exclusively reserved time slots and consistent quality control.</p>
    <h3 class="sectionTitle" style="font-size:1.2rem">Exclusively reserved service windows</h3>
    <p class="sectionPara">Every cleaning appointment is carried out within a fixed time window reserved specifically for your property. That creates focus, predictability and reliability.</p>
    <ul class="sectionList">
      <li>100% focus on your property</li>
      <li>No parallel assignments</li>
      <li>Reliable execution</li>
      <li>Visual check for anything unusual, if relevant</li>
      <li>Transparent communication</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="sectionPara">We deliberately look after only a limited number of properties so that this standard can be maintained at all times. Quality survives where concentration and capacity are protected.</p>
    <h3 class="sectionTitle" style="font-size:1.2rem">Planning creates confidence</h3>
    <p class="sectionPara">When occupancy phases, arrivals and reserved service windows are aligned, the result is a stable and predictable process: fewer questions, less stress, consistent quality and a refined impression with every arrival. Security is not a coincidence. It is the result of a system.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="contentBlock">
    <h2 class="sectionTitle">For owners who do not leave peace of mind to chance</h2>
    <p class="sectionPara">This service is for owners who want more than a clean property. It is for those who understand that condition creates perception. A refined home does not need to impress loudly. It convinces through consistency, care and the quiet confidence of a residence that is perfectly prepared.</p>
    <p class="sectionPara">That is exactly what Luxury Services is designed for: a calm, elegant extension of Property Care for private residences in Madeira that deserve more.</p>
  </div>
</div>
